<p>This is a project that needs to be completed so as to ease the onboarding process, removing Christopher from the loop and making it as easy as entering the required information into a form and having it processed for all systems. It was spec'd in July/August 2011 essentially. Serv1 and the wiki have been phased out. The ticket system was migrated and all of the pieces have been put into place for this to happen with the exception of single sign-on but that has been delayed.</p>